OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with bright spells for most.
OL,7,FRemaining dry overnight with clear
OL,8,Fspells developing, although as the
OL,9,Fwind eases light this may allow some
OL,10,Ffog patches to form in rural spots.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA dry day with any early
OL,13,Fcloud clearing to give plenty of sunny
OL,14,Fspells. Becoming warm or very warm,
OL,15,Fespecially away from southern coasts.
OL,16,FLight winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
