OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FVery
OL,6,Fwarm for most during this period, hot
OL,7,Fin places, with plenty of sunshine.
OL,8,FIsolated showers may develop in the
OL,9,Ffar east on Saturday.
